beer.beer_description:
A rugged IPA, loaded with more hops than any other Little Creatures beer... our  IPA packs a serious hoppy punch. 

Style: India Pale Ale

Malt: 
Pale Ale, Carapils, Munich, Cararye

Hops: 
EKG (UK) bittering, Vic Secret (AUS) whirlpool, Southern Cross Cones (NZ), Amarillo (US) dry hop pellets. 

Pairing: 
Strong spicy foods, classic with a curry; mild blue cheeses, bold desserts.
